text: Nassarius jeanmartini is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Nassariidae, the Nassa mud snails or dog whelks. ==Description== The length of the shell varies between 5 mm and 8 mm. ==Distribution== This species occurs in the Indian Ocean off Mauritius and La Réunion. ==References== ==External links== * Category:Nassariidae Category:Gastropods described in 2006
title: Nassarius jeanmartini
